name: YouAuction
overview:
We’re a free Online Social Market where you can buy, sell or advertise online to public and friends through video and pictures. We,re a socially-driven marketplace where you can create a profile and list your items. Our goal is to make it easier to keep up with your friends and associated business within your community

YouAuction was developed to be a place where people can go to make friends, share videos,photos, network personally and professionally, share thoughts, buy and sell items, and locate services. We believe in a sense of community and understand that the community is a direct reflection of its members.

Our goal is to give people the power to sell and make the selling process more open and connected. We want to make the site a tool to communicate and share information on your product or services with other people online.
